    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A dense, hard marble from Belgium, considered the best black marble for carving due to its deep color and lack of veins and streaks. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
